msgid "Design and implementation of test automation frameworks using C#, Java, and JavaScript. Experience with Selenium, Playwright, Appium, and WinAppDriver."
msgstr "Ontwerp en implementatie van testautomatiseringsframeworks met C#, Java en JavaScript. Ervaring met Selenium, Playwright, Appium en WinAppDriver."

msgid "Integration of automated tests into CI/CD pipelines using Azure DevOps, with focus on improving test coverage, reducing execution time, and increasing release stability."
msgstr "Integratie van geautomatiseerde tests in CI/CD-pipelines met Azure DevOps, met focus op het verbeteren van testdekking, verkorting van uitvoeringstijd en verhoging van release-stabiliteit."

msgid "Experience in API testing, microservices validation, and SQL-based verification within Agile development environments. Focus on maintainable automation solutions and improving QA processes through test automation."
msgstr "Ervaring met API testing, microservices-validatie en SQL-gebaseerde verificatie binnen Agile ontwikkelomgevingen. Focus op onderhoudbare automatiseringsoplossingen en het verbeteren van QA-processen via testautomatisering."

